## Payment Gateway Testing for Global Shiksha

### Overview
As part of my first role at Global Shiksha, I was responsible for testing the payment gateway integration of the educational e-commerce platform. The payment gateway supported multiple payment methods, including UPI, credit/debit cards, and net banking. This testing ensured secure, reliable, and seamless payment processing for users.

### Responsibilities
- Prepared the test plan for the payment gateway module.
- Designed and executed test cases for various payment scenarios.
- Created a traceability matrix to ensure complete coverage of requirements.
- Performed API testing for transaction validation using Postman.
- Logged and tracked bugs using Bugzilla.
